# Responsive Web Layout

A modern responsive website built using HTML5 and CSS3 with Flexbox, Media Queries, Responsive Navigation, and Mobile-Friendly UI Design.

## 🚀 Live Demo


responsive-web-layout-4xuf5qe7h-rockaditya.vercel.app



---

## 📌 Features

* Responsive Web Design
* Modern UI Layout
* Sticky Navigation Bar
* Hero Section
* Skills Cards Section
* About Section
* CTA Section
* Responsive Footer
* Mobile-Friendly Design
* Flexbox Layout
* Media Queries

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* HTML5
* CSS3
* Flexbox
* Media Queries

---

## 📱 Responsive Design

This project is fully responsive for:

* Mobile Devices
* Tablets
* Laptops
* Desktop Screens

